<title>yswʿ mwjwd lsẖfạỷk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mạ tqwlsẖ ạlwqt ʿdy wạlḥạl bqạlẗ snyn dy ạydyn yswʿ btsẖfy kl yạỷs ḥzyn

[V2]
 mạ hw ạlly bysẖwfk wytḥnn ʿlyk ạlnạs ysẖfwk yʿdwạ whw yndh ʿlyk

[V3]
 tẖq fyẗ wqwm hw bynạdyk

[V4]
 qrạr - yswʿ mwjwd lsẖfạỷk qwm bsrʿẗ ạndẗ ʿlyẗ

[V5]
 dh mhmạ kạn syỷ ḥạlk ạydyn yswʿ tdạwyẗ

[V6]
 2- mạtqwlsẖ ẓrwfy qạsyẗ wạlkl trkny wḥyd dh ạlhk sẖạyf ḥạltk wṣạnʿ lk ạmr jdyd

[V7]
 mạhw ạlly ʿsẖạnk ạtnạzl ʿn smạh ʿlsẖạn yqwl qrblh mnẗ hw ạlḥyạẗ

[V8]
 tẖq fyẗ wqwm hw bynạdyk

[V9]
 3- mạ tqwlsẖ ạldnyạ ḍlmẗ wmsẖ sẖạyf gẖyr ạnyyn dh ạlhk ʿndẗ sʿạdtk wmntẓrk mn snyyn

[V10]
 ạlly ẓhr jwh ạlnạr wʿmrẗ mạ trk wlạdh ḥty ạldm ạlly sạl mḥfwẓ ʿndẗ fy smạỷẗ

[V11]
 tẖq fyẗ wqwm ạtmtʿ blqạỷẗ

[V12]
 4- mạ tqwlsẖ mạlysẖ rjạʾ wạlhy kẖlạṣ nsyny ạlly mʿạk fy̱ kl lḥẓẗ byqwl ḥạfẓk ymyny

[V13]
 dh brwḥẗ qryb mnk wạqrb mnk ạlyẗ wbynzʿ hmwmk ʿnk wbymsḥ dmʿ ʿynyk

[V14]
 tẖq fyẗ wqwm hw bynạdyk</lyrics>
